            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Valerius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Ser</abbr><ex>gia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>H</abbr><ex cert="low">i</ex>er</expan>(apolis<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <expan><abbr>tub</abbr><ex>icen</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Apoll</abbr><ex>inaris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>XVI <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>XXXVI <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>vivite felices <lb n="9"/>quibus est dat<lb break="no" n="10"/>a longior <expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>ora</abbr></expan> <lb n="11"/>vixi ego dum licu<lb break="no" n="12"/>it dulciter ad Supe<lb break="no" n="13"/>ros dicite si merui <lb n="14"/>sit tibi ter<expan><ex>r</ex><abbr>a</abbr></expan> <lb n="15"/>levis
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Unterhalb des Inschriftfeldes tuba und ein weiterer Gegenstand (Dämpfer für die tuba?). Metrik: Daktylen (Z. 8-15).</p>
            </div>
